\id PRO - Djambarrpuyngu Scriptures 
\h Djambatj dhäruk 
\toc3 Djambatj dhäruk 
\toc2 Djambatj dhäruk 
\toc1 Djambatj dhäruk 
\mt1 Djambatj dhäruk  
\c 3  
\p
\v 5 Nheny dhu ga ŋunhi ŋayaŋu-ṉiṉ’thundja God-Waŋarrwalnydja yuwalkkuman yan. Ga yaka gi märr-yuwalkthi nhokiyingal nhe marŋgi-lakaranhaminyaraw, bili yaka nhe dhuwal marŋgi bukmakkuny nhaku malaŋuw.   